#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:2
msgid "数据管道 (DataPipe)"
msgstr "Data Pipeline (DataPipe)"

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:4
msgid "FreeRec 基于 torchdata 的 DataPipe 机制构建了链式数据处理管道， 通过方法链将数据从原始格式转换为模型可用的张量批次。"
msgstr "FreeRec builds chained data processing pipelines based on torchdata's DataPipe mechanism, transforming data from raw format to model-ready tensor batches through method chaining."

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:8
msgid "核心理念"
msgstr "Core Concept"

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:10
msgid "数据管道由一系列 **Processor** 组成，每个 Processor 消费上游数据并产出处理后的数据， 形成一条从数据源到最终张量的流水线："
msgstr "The data pipeline consists of a series of **Processors**, where each Processor consumes upstream data and produces processed data, forming a pipeline from data source to final tensors:"

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:19
msgid "所有 Processor 通过 **方法链** (method chaining) 串联："
msgstr "All Processors are chained together via **method chaining**:"

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:35
msgid "类层次结构"
msgstr "Class Hierarchy"

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:45
msgid "**Source** ：管道的起点，从 RecDataSet 中读取数据并封装为可迭代对象"
msgstr "**Source**: The starting point of the pipeline; reads data from RecDataSet and wraps it as an iterable"

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:46
msgid "**PostProcessor** ：所有中间处理节点的基类，包装上游管道并逐条处理"
msgstr "**PostProcessor**: Base class for all intermediate processing nodes; wraps the upstream pipeline and processes items one by one"

#: ../../tutorials/datapipe.rst:47
msgid "**SampleMultiplexer** ：按权重从多个数据源交替采样"
msgstr "**SampleMultiplexer**: Alternately samples from multiple data sources according to weights"

